net.smartcosmos.pojo.integration

Class NotificationEndpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.smartcosmos.pojo.base.DomainResource<T>
      • net.smartcosmos.pojo.base.ReferentialObject<INotificationEndpoint>
        • net.smartcosmos.pojo.integration.NotificationEndpoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAccountContext, IDomainResource<INotificationEndpoint>, IMoniker, INamedObject<INotificationEndpoint>, IReferentialObject, IUrnNamespace, INotificationEndpoint

    public class NotificationEndpoint
extends ReferentialObject<INotificationEndpoint>
implements INotificationEndpoint
    Represents an HTTP/S integration endpoint POJO that SMART COSMOS uses to push SMART COSMOS events in JSON form in near real-time. These endpoints are used for back office integration and 3rd party extension integration.
